OL,6,FThe new Bishop of Sodor and Man says
OL,7,Fshe is 'very excited and honoured' to
OL,8,Ftake on her new role in the .
OL,10,FThe Venerable Patricia Hillas will
OL,11,Ftake over from the Right Reverend
OL,12,FPeter Eagles, following his retirement
OL,13,Fin October 2023.
OL,15,FRt Rev Hillas will officially take on
OL,16,Fher new role, following her
OL,17,Fconsecration as a bishop at York
OL,18,FCathedral on 10 October.
