OL,3,CRevd Patricia Hillas appointed as next
OL,4,CBishop of Sodor and Man
OL,6,FSodor and Man is the smallest diocese
OL,7,Fin the Church of England, with a total
OL,8,Fof 45 churches and 27 parishes.
OL,10,FTricia was ordained in 2002, working
OL,11,Fin the Diocese of London, until she
OL,12,Fbecame vicar of St Barnabas in
OL,13,FNortholt and Sub-Dean for Northolt,
OL,14,FPerivale and Greenford.
