OL,3,CRevd Patricia Hillas appointed as next
OL,4,CBishop of Sodor and Man
OL,6,FIn November 2013, Tricia was appointed
OL,7,Fas Canon Pastor at St Paul's
OL,8,FCathedral, before joining the
OL,9,FSpeaker's Office as Chaplain in 2019,
OL,10,Fwhere she was most visible taking part
OL,11,Fin the Speaker's procession and
OL,12,Fconducting daily prayers in the
OL,13,FCommons' chamber.
OL,15,FShe also provided pastoral care for
OL,16,FMembers and staff of the Palace of
OL,17,FWestminster ` and was formerly Priest
OL,18,Fin Charge of St Mary at Hill in the
OL,19,FCity of London.
