OL,3,CRevd Patricia Hillas appointed as next
OL,4,CBishop of Sodor and Man
OL,6,FSpeaking on her appointment, the
OL,7,FSpeaker of the House of Commons said
OL,8,Fhe "could not think of a kinder or
OL,9,Fmore engaging person than Tricia".
OL,11,F"Tricia has been an amazing colleague
OL,12,Fwho has been at my side during some of
OL,13,Fthe most turbulent and challenging
OL,14,Ftimes, but also among the most
OL,15,Fcelebratory," he added.
