OL,3,CRevd Patricia Hillas appointed as next
OL,4,CBishop of Sodor and Man
OL,6,F"Together we have faced the impact on
OL,7,Fthe parliamentary community of Covid,
OL,8,Fthe murder of our much-loved colleague
OL,9,FSir David Amess, the deaths of Her
OL,10,FMajesty Queen Elizabeth, her husband
OL,11,Fthe Duke of Edinburgh, the Coronation
OL,12,Fof His Majesty King Charles III, and
OL,13,Feven the death of my dear father.
OL,15,F"We have introduced opportunities to
OL,16,Fmark Holocaust Memorial Day, Armed
OL,17,FForces Day, the Constituency Garden of
OL,18,FRemembrance, Commonwealth Day, and of
OL,19,Fcourse, the many Christmas and multi-
OL,20,Ffaith events we host for the
OL,21,Fparliamentary community.
